{"thag2.27:0.1":"Theragatha 2.27 ","thag2.27:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.27:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.27:0.4":"Nandakattheragatha ","thag2.27:1.1":"“Yathapi bhaddo ajanno, ","thag2.27:1.2":"khalitva patititthati; ","thag2.27:1.3":"Bhiyyo laddhana samvegam, ","thag2.27:1.4":"adino vahate dhuram. ","thag2.27:2.1":"Evam dassanasampannam, ","thag2.27:2.2":"sammasambuddhasavakam; ","thag2.27:2.3":"Ajaniyam mam dharetha, ","thag2.27:2.4":"puttam buddhassa orasan”ti. ","thag2.27:2.5":"… Nandako thero …. "}